and for expressing yourself.

41:16.808 --> 41:18.076
Thank you, Barbara.

41:18.109 --> 41:20.545
We'll be right back
after this message.

41:20.579 --> 41:21.813
<i>And we're out.</i>

41:21.847 --> 41:23.081
<i>That was wonderful.
Thank you.</i>

41:23.114 --> 41:24.683
Thank you.

41:24.716 --> 41:26.885
